github.grovre.interfaces

Interface AtomicCapable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MutableBoolean, MutableByte, MutableInteger, MutableLong, MutableShort

    public interface AtomicCapable
    Any Mutable object that is inherently supported by Java's atomic package will implement this interface and be able to provide an easy way of getting the number or non-number variable as an Atomic.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      java.lang.Object asAtomic()
      Formed in implementing classes to represent Atomic types of numbers and some non-number types.
